name: Border Canary
description: Border Canaries are the result of the evolution of common canary.

name: Affenpinscher
description: Loyal, curious, and famously amusing, this almost-human toy dog is fearless.

description: An immensely strong, heavy-duty worker of spitz type

name: Birman Cat
description: The Birman is a cat of distinction as well as legend. With their exotic ancestry, luxurious pointed coats, “white gloved” paws and mesmerizing blue eyes, this is a breed with undeniable charisma

name: Bengal Cat
description: Bengal Cats are curious and confident with the tameness of a domestic tabby and the beauty of an Asian Leopard Cat.

name: Black-throated Sparrow
description: Black-throated Sparrows are small birds often living in the southwestern US and Mexico

name: Cairn Terrier
description: Cairn Terriers are happy, busy little earthdogs originally bred to fearlessly root out foxes

name: Budgerigars
description: Budgerigars are small birds that are long tailed and feed on seeds. They are native to the desert parts of Australia

name: Savannah Cat
description: The Savannah Cat’s personality is playful, adventurous and loyal. Unlike most cats, she loves to play in water and can even be trained to walk on a leash and play fetch
